Scenario 1 : Given I am logged in as Advisor and or Farmer -(test reject scenario)
If an agent, I select AMS from Agent tools and select a client to go to Farmer Dashboard
If a farmer, I see AMS panel on Farmer Dashboard
And I press Respond to Findings
And I see warning at top of screen
Red Warning Message to display at top of screen " Actions and/or failure to take action in response to AMS Notifications may impact all area based scheme payments. Please respond below"
And i see quick filter - View all, Action Required
And i see columns
Red exclaimation/green tick (no header)
Townland
Parcel no,/Plot ref.
AMS status
AMS findings
Accept/Reject findings?
Claimed area (ha)
Parcel use
Action (view map icon)
And I see a list of all parcels – Reds only Round1
And there is a Actions View map icon on the end of each parcel line
And the AMS findings column is populated with Artificial Surface
And I see my red parcels with a red symbol for response required
And i see bottom left page AMS status legend with Red non compliant
And I select a parcel to reject findings
Side Drawer opens
See Edit parcel (bolded) top (styling as per figma)
See townland and Parcel No./Plot Ref. and can navigate between parcels
Red symbol at top of side drawer with message "missing mandatory information"
And i see Question Do you accept/reject findings?
And i select reject
