And I save changes
And i see a toast message in green "You have successfully updated details for Parcel No X"
And then i close side drawer
And i return to AMS screen
And the red symbol on parcel (left side) is now gone
And I see submit button (if i have responded to all ) Dont submit
And if i try to submit (with not all responded to) I see a red warning

